---
---

<section class="newsletter">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>GET RINGSIDE</h2>
    <p>Sign up for KPL Insider — fight announcements, betting odds, and exclusive content delivered to your inbox every week. Plus a free digital copy of <em>"Your Kidneys & You: A Fighter's Guide."</em></p>
    <div class="newsletter-form">
      <input type="email" class="newsletter-input" placeholder="Enter your email address" />
      <button class="btn btn-primary">SIGN UP</button>
    </div>
    <div class="newsletter-disclaimer">By subscribing, you acknowledge that kidney punching involves inherent risks and agree to our Terms of Service.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .newsletter p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .newsletter-input {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 250px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .newsletter-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .newsletter-disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
